{"id": 2516, "genre": 1000, "title": "你觉得如何对待女性才算得上一个“当代绅士”？", "description": "补上“尊重”这一课，比学得一百条未经推敲的“女士优先”类法则更重要。", "record_count": 40846, "comment_count": 94, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180910174511GaDNgfrXstVS1WHw.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-09-11T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 4669, "title": "你觉得如何对待女性才算得上一个“当代绅士”？", "content": "你觉得哪些关于“如何对待女性”的规范，符合一名“当代绅士”？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 298122, "content": "接触前先打招呼：“我能坐这吗/方便接电话吗”", "image": "img/option/option/20180910174949ycUgRXEx1IF8W4Ko.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 298123, "content": "被明确拒绝后不再纠缠，更不转而侮辱对方", "image": "img/option/option/20180910175117id01jRPWpDhnAFMQ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 298125, "content": "不到处吹嘘性经历，不对不熟悉的女性讲黄色笑话", "image": "img/option/option/201809101752112PCIi4J0SlDZseBX.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 298126, "content": "不主动对女性有肢体接触，握手等礼仪等女性先伸手", "image": "img/option/option/20180910175311oPhFSDyCgETdsG62.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 298128, "content": "尊重对方改变心意的决定，而不是跳脚“女人就是善变”", "image": "img/option/option/20180910175451XmOF1HLNr2CfdDkB.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 298130, "content": "亲密行为先征得对方同意", "image": "img/option/option/20180910175659jfSeqgKo7FvW5Ds3.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 298131, "content": "在拥挤/危险的环境下主动保护女性", "image": "img/option/option/201809101757398uPYvqFICyoOKLT6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 298133, "content": "清晰但不唐突地表达爱意，不自说自话强迫对方接受", "image": "img/option/option/20180910180131evYVJBA6qwPDTmht.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}